OL,6,FThe CCRC previously said it has
OL,7,Freferred 11 cases which relied on his
OL,8,Fevidence.
OL,10,FHe died of a heart attack in prison in
OL,11,F1982 at the age of 37.
OL,13,FMr Mehmet, who died in 2021, and Mr
OL,14,FPeterkin, who died in 1991, were both
OL,15,Fsentenced to nine months in prison in
OL,16,F1977, over the theft of parcels from
OL,17,Fthe Bricklayers Arms goods depot in
OL,18,Fsouth London, where they worked.
