OL,6,FThey said the items found in their
OL,7,Fpossession had been planted, and that
OL,8,Fany admissions said to have been made
OL,9,Fby them had been fabricated by the
OL,10,Fpolice.
OL,12,FIn 1980, Ridgewell was jailed for
OL,13,Fseven years for stealing property
OL,14,Fworth #364,000 from the same site,
OL,15,Fwhile two of his colleagues were
OL,16,Fsentenced to six and two years,
OL,17,Frespectively.
