OL,7,Finvestigating the "historical racist
OL,8,Fand corrupt practices" of Ridgewell,
OL,9,Fwhose corruption has led to the
OL,10,Fconvictions of members of the so-
OL,11,Fcalled Oval Four and Stockwell Six
OL,12,Fbeing overturned in recent years.
OL,14,FNine other convictions relating to
OL,15,FRidgewell have previously been quashed.
