OL,6,FITV London News approached the British
OL,7,FTransport Police for a comment, Chief
OL,8,FConstable Lucy D'Orsi, said: "My
OL,9,Fcolleagues and I are profoundly sorry
OL,10,Fto all those affected by DS
OL,11,FRidgewell's atrocious actions and the
OL,12,Ftrauma that victims and their families
OL,13,Fsuffered as a result.
OL,15,F"The identification of DS Ridgewell's
OL,16,Fvictims has always been important to
OL,17,Fus and we are pleased that the
OL,18,FCriminal Cases Review Commission have
OL,19,Fidentified two further victims.
